==== NodeJs Back End start from below ====
1. npm init -y
2. sudo npm i express dotenv nodemon
3. sudo npm i mongoose
4. sudo npm i dotenv
5. sudo npm i uuid
6. sudo npm i body-parser morgan
7. sudo npm i cookie-parser
8. sudo npm i express-validator
9. sudo npm i express-jwt jsonwebtoken
10. sudo npm i formidable lodash

================ Braintree token API ==============
sudo npm i braintree


   

==== Reactjs Front End start from below ====

11. sudo npm i cors
12. sudo npx create-react-app ecommerce-frontend --use-npm
13. sudo npm install react-router-dom
14. sudo npm i query-string
15. sudo npm i moment
16. sudo npm install react-alice-carousel

================ Braintree React ==============
sudo npm i braintree-web-drop-in-react braintree-web

Best Banner for ReactJs -- https://github.com/akiran/react-slick

16. sudo npm install react-slick --save

sudo npm uninstall react-slick --save


============= Hub Spot form ================

npm install --save react-hubspot-form








